### Create a campaign (success)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/exception2/campaigns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "camp-001",
  "remain": 100000,
  "dailyQuota": 50000
}

### Create invalid (blank id)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/exception2/campaigns
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "",
  "remain": 100000,
  "dailyQuota": 50000
}

### Then charge (if created)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/exception2/campaigns/camp-001/charge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000
}
